<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 0 (10 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Mimicry.</em></strong> The raven can mimic simple sounds it has heard, such as a person whispering, a baby crying, or an animal chittering. A creature that hears the sounds can tell they are imitations with a successful DC 10 Wisdom (Insight) check.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Beak.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 1 piercing damage.</p>

